.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aPolitical sciencexPhilosophy. 4aPhilosophie. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitische Philosophie. 4aPolitische Theorie. 4aPoststrukturalismus. 4aPsychoanalytische Theorie. 4aSymbol. 4aZeichentheorie. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh  aPhilosophy.  aPolitical Philosophy.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Theory.  aPost-structuralism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2000-2009z97831104633470 cprintz978389942655740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839406557?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839406557423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839406557/original  a978-3-11-046334-7  transcript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2000-2009c2000d2009  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009